{"tid":48353,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【強國乜都假】深圳馬拉松得獎「女跑手」 驚揭係男兒身！　","createTime":"2016-12-21T04:39:41.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-21T06:50:47.000Z","uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"297ea693222696e2525c267879e422718f67facb","tid":48353,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T04:39:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20161221&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=56073562\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20161221%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D56073562&d=%2BajzBnAb0PlQEQmw%2Fg88umN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=97ddba9a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20161221%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D56073562&h=ed4a815a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20161221&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=56073562</a><br />\n2016深圳國際馬拉松周日落幕，但在周一（19日）成績公示之後，有跑友發現比賽中有人疑似「替跑」，更指女子馬拉松得獎跑手竟然是男跑手代跑。<br />\n幾天前，中國田協才出了通知，嚴打替跑現象，並且準備對違規者給予終身禁賽的重罰。然後只過了一天，在深圳國際馬拉松中，就發現替跑。有跑友爆料稱，在深圳市民特別獎女子組前十選手中，有兩位參賽選手的照片顯示是男子跑者，分別是B0575號和B0800號。本次深馬的參賽號碼B開頭組別為女子全程馬拉松選手，男子跑者使用B開頭的號碼布，很明顯不合理。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ym0Q282.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYm0Q282.jpg&h=06226a0a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cf5df0be44f57c15b0c7ad7d423dc4e9da3a7942","tid":48353,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T04:45:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20161221&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=56073562\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20161221%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D56073562&d=%2BajzBnAb0PlQEQmw%2Fg88umN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=97ddba9a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20161221%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D56073562&h=ed4a815a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">h